New Records: Fred VanVleet finished 10 of 11 from the floor, including 9 for 9 from inside the arc
Key Match Events: Fred VanVleet recorded his first double-double of the season
Jalen Green and Alperen Sengun combined for 37 points
The Spurs were undone by their 20 turnovers, which Houston converted into 20 points
Victor Wembanyama scored 15 points but missed 5 of 6 3-pointers, including his first five
Miscellaneous Highlights: The bench trio of Amen Thompson, Tari Eason and Jock Landale tallied 31 points on 14-for-23 shooting
Others: Houston finished with a 127-100 victory over the visiting San Antonio Spurs
